    <id>http://example.com/2023/04/20/%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3Hexo%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5SSH%E7%9A%8410054%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</id>
    <published>2023-04-20T04:31:45.359Z</published>
    <updated>2023-04-20T04:30:18.392Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="解决Hexo-连接的SSH-10054-问题"><a href="#解决Hexo-连接的SSH-10054-问题" class="headerlink" title="解决Hexo 连接的SSH 10054 问题"></a>解决Hexo 连接的SSH 10054 问题</h2><p>方式一：在命令行输入</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global http.sslVerify &quot;false&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>方式二：配置SSH Key（一劳永逸解决问题）</p><ol><li><p>在命令行分别输入</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name 你的姓名</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email 你的邮箱地址</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>生成SSH密钥</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C 你的邮箱地址</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在系统盘个人用户文件夹下找到.ssh文件打开</p><img                       lazyload                     alt="image"                     data-src="C:\Users\44382\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230420122101751.png"                      alt="image-20230420122101751"                  ></li><li><p>将id_rsa.pub文件（公钥）内的内容全部复制粘贴到GitHub</p></li><li><p>在GitHub个人设置处找到SSH and GPG key 进行绑定</p><p><img                       lazyload                     alt="image"                     data-src="C:\Users\44382\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230420122436731.png"                      alt="image-20230420122436731"                ></p></li><li><p>将公钥复制到Key处点击Add SSH key 进行添加</p><img                       lazyload                     alt="image"                     data-src="C:\Users\44382\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230420122501922.png"                      alt="image-20230420122501922" style="zoom:80%;"                 ></li><li><p>绑定成功后在命令行输入查看连接状态，即可一劳永逸完成绑定工作</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img                       lazyload                     alt="image"                     data-src="C:\Users\44382\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230420122754571.png"                      alt="image-20230420122754571"                ></p></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h2 id=&quot;解决Hexo-连接的SSH-10054-问题&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#解决Hexo-连接的SSH-10054-问题&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;解决Hexo 连接的SSH 10054 问题&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;解决Hexo 连接的SSH 10054 </summary>
      
    
    
    
    
